ctlogo.function

Interface Function

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFunction, AcosFunction, AsinFunction, Atan2Function, AtanFunction, BackwardFunction, CleanFunction, ClearScreenFunction, CosFunction, ForwardFunction, HideTurtleFunction, LeftFunction, MakeFunction, PendownFunction, PenupFunction, PrintFunction, RightFunction, SetxFunction, SetxyFunction, SetyFunction, ShowTurtleFunction, SinFunction, TanFunction, XcorFunction, YcorFunction

    public interface Function
    An object representing a Logo function.

    A function may accept zero or more parameter, and a funtion must have a pre-defined default parameter number

    Author:
    Paul Yang
